T { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4a66605c-8803-4ad5-b894-f8859d3ccc49\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e99b11c6-06d5-11f0-af68-67cbd21ec5db\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>샘플 수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e99b11c7-06d5-11f0-af68-19185818c97d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 3개 이상 (생산은 4개, 납품은 3개 진행했습니다.)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4408ec58-0718-40a6-ad34-5775ed3b934c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e99b11c8-06d5-11f0-af68-01b068076a13\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>금액</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e99b38d9-06d5-11f0-af68-6d8f836c6104\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 금액은 공개하지 않겠습니다. 하지만 가장 합리적인 금액을 최저가로 제안 드렸습니다. 고객님이 바쁘다고 절대 불합리한 가격으로 제안 드리지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-529a38b6-0ac9-4c70-acd9-b4a29becb222\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e99b38da-06d5-11f0-af68-7db327aa89bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223779533279#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
